Company Overview of MFS Meridian Funds - Global Equity Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
MFS Meridian Funds - Global Equity Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched by MFS Investment Management Company (Lux) S.à.r.l. The fund is managed by Massachusetts Financial Services Company. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. The fund seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It makes its investments in growth and value stocks of companies across all market capitalization with a focus on large cap stocks. The fund employs fundamental analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against MSCI World Index. MFS Meridian Funds - Global Equity Fund wa...
MFS Meridian Funds - Global Equity Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched by MFS Investment Management Company (Lux) S.à.r.l. The fund is managed by Massachusetts Financial Services Company. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. The fund seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It makes its investments in growth and value stocks of companies across all market capitalization with a focus on large cap stocks. The fund employs fundamental analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against MSCI World Index. MFS Meridian Funds - Global Equity Fund was formed on March 12, 1999 and is domiciled in Luxembourg.
